Nwaanyị a ma ama na-eme ihe nkiri bụ Rachal Oniga anwụọla dịka ọ gbachara afọ iri isii na anọ.
Onyeisi otu ndị na-eme ihe nkiri na Naịjirịa bụ Actors Guild of Nigeria (AGN) bụ Emeka Rollas sị na nwa nwaanyị ahụ gwara odeakwụkwọ ya na ọ bụ eziokwu.
Ihe ise ị maghị maka Ernest Asuzu lara mmụọ
"Nwa ya gwara odeakwụkwọ na nne ya nwụrụ n'ihe dịka elekere iri nke abalị 30 Julaị, 2021.
Emeka sị na ha amatabeghi ihe butere ọwwụ nwaanyị ahụ.
Ihe i kwesịrị ịma maka Rachel Oniga
Ebe foto si, Rachel Oniga/Instagram
Rachel Oniga bụ a nwafọ obodo Eku dị na Delta Steetị
A  mụrụ ya na Legọs n'ọnwa Mee afọ 1957 n'Ebutte Metta dị na Legọs Steetị.
Ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ n'ụlọakwụkwọ Princess Girls dị n'Abula Oja nke Yaba, Legọs.
Ọ mụrụ ụmụ atọ mana ya na di ya gbara alụkwaghịm tupu ọ nwụọ.
Ọ rụrụ ọrụ dịka 'Computer Programmer'.
Ọ malitere ime ihe onyonyo n'afọ 1993.
Ụfọdụ ihe nkiri ndị o mere gụnyere; Sango (1997), Owo Blow (1997), Passion of Mind (2004), Royal Hibiscus (2017), Wedding Party (2018), My Village People (2021) dgz.
Ihe ndị mmadụ na-ekwu maka ọnwụ Rachel
Onyeisi otu na-eme ihe nyonyo na Theatre bụ Jide Kosoko sị ya "laa n'udo"
Hilda Dokubo tinyekwara ọnụ sị na ọ na-akpọkaarị ya "Nne m nne m". Ọ sị na eluigwe nwere anya ukwu mgbe ụfọdụ maka ọnwụ Rachel.
